Private Events
Home
/ Private Events
Allow us to host your upcoming social gathering or corporate event. 

Private events tailored to groups of 16 or more are available, ensuring an intimate and exclusive experience. Immerse yourself in the beauty of the Orlando sunsets while creating lasting memories.  

Please
complete our private event inquiry form here
and one of our sales specialists will get back to you within 5 business days.

For parties of 15 or less, please search for availability
here

TUESDAY THROUGH FRIDAY from 11AM-3PM
AC EXPRESS LUNCH
Make the most of your lunch hour with the AC Sky Bar's express lunch, which includes an assortment of delicious options and one non-alcoholic beverage for just $18, all backed by a 20-minute service guarantee. 

We're committed to prompt and incredible service, so don't delay and join us for lunch today!

EVERY SATURDAY & SUNDAY from 11AM-3PM
SKY-HIGH BRUNCH
Rise and dine at AC Sky Bar, Downtown Orlandoâs premier rooftop brunch destination! Indulge in delicious chef-crafted bites, sip on signature handcrafted mimosas and cocktails, and take in the breathtaking skyline views from the cityâs best rooftop. 

Whether youâre catching up with friends, celebrating the weekend, or just craving a stylish brunch with a view, AC Sky Bar is the place to be. With a vibrant atmosphere, premium flavors, and the perfect mix of sophistication and fun, your brunch experience just got elevated.

EVERY WEDNESDAY from 4PM-7PM
WINE DOWN WEDNESDAY
Unwind above the city with Wine Down Wednesday at AC Hotel Sky Bar! Enjoy a curated selection of three reds, three whites, and one sparkling wine, expertly poured at your table. 

For just $25+ per person, you can sip and savor while exploring perfect pairings from our special menu. A dedicated team will ensure a seamless experience, with a rinse station available for fresh pours. 

Relax, indulge, and elevate your midweek routine with great wine, delicious bites, and stunning rooftop views. Join us and toast to the perfect evening!
